languages.text: "Пожалуйста, пропустите. Я всего лишь бедная девушка. У меня нечего брать!"
"Please, let me through. I'm just a poor girl. I don't have anything!"

languages.text: “求求你们，放我过去吧。我只是个可怜的姑娘，什么都没有！”
languages.original_text: "Please, let me through. I'm just a poor girl. I don't have anything!"

traits.locale_text: “求求你们，放我过去吧。我只是个可怜的姑娘，什么都没有！”

languages.text: 「どうか通らせてください。私はただの貧しい娘です。何も持ってません！」
languages.original_text: "Please, let me through. I'm just a poor girl. I don't have anything!"

traits.locale_text: 「どうか通らせてください。私はただの貧しい娘です。何も持ってません！」

languages.text: «Déjeme pasar, por favor. Soy pobre como una rata. ¡No tengo nada de valor!».
languages.original_text: "Please, let me through. I'm just a poor girl. I don't have anything!"

traits.locale_text: «Déjeme pasar, por favor. Soy pobre como una rata. ¡No tengo nada de valor!».

languages.text: "Bırakın geçeyim. Fakir bir kızcağızım. Hiçbir şeyim yok!"

traits.locale_text: "Bırakın geçeyim. Fakir bir kızcağızım. Hiçbir şeyim yok!"

languages.text: « Laissez-moi passer, s'il vous plaît. Je ne suis qu'une fille du peuple. Je n'ai rien qui puisse vous intéresser ! »
languages.original_text: "Please, let me through. I'm just a poor girl. I don't have anything!"

languages.text: "Bitte. Lasst mich durch. Ich bin nur ein armes Mädchen. Ich habe doch nichts."
